{"word":"μετριάζω","slug":"μετριάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μετριάζω</b></el> <el>(μετριάζω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μέτριος'><el>μέτριος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be moderate, keep measure</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to moderate, regulate, control</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>moderari</el>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}